article_title: Women’s rights, education focus at Clinton event in Rock Hill
article_text:
Rock Hill first of three stops for former first daughter Chelsea Clinton

Healthcare, women’s rights and college education were hot topics Eve

Event draws more than 100 Clinton supporters
